<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sincronizar Calendário via WhatsApp</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            color: #1c1e21;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            max-width: 380px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 { font-weight: 600; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { color: #65676B; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.5; }
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: #25D366;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.2);
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #25D366;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        button:hover { background-color: #1DA851; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Seu Google Calendar no WhatsApp</h1>
        <p>Preencha seu número e autorize o calendário. Receba as notificações diárias de seus compromissos no seu celular toda manhã de forma orgânica e silenciosa.</p>
        <form action="/connect" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="whatsappNumber" placeholder="Número (DDI, DDD e Telefone)" required>
            <button type="submit">Conectar via Google</button>
        </form>
        <footer style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 11px; color: #999;">
            <a href="/privacidade" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">Política de Privacidade</a>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
